reviews.text:
2 Jan 19: we went there around 12:30, not many people until 12:45, almost full house after 13:00. No 10% surcharge for lunch and the lunch set with drinks and dessert. 

The risotto is small portion, but it is just good for me, the spaghetti is large portion and my colleague (male) could not finished the whole dish, the potato chips are over cooked. The desserts came to us just right after we finished our meal, the taste is not really good as imagine. Overall service is good and quick response and price is acceptable and place is clean and cozy.
1500 HKD for valentines, no service, crowdy and the food is cold
Good service,  good serving size,  and reasonably priced lunch for the area.  Taste of the baked Spag Bol, was commendable.
no air conditioning when we had lunch there
The food is delicious and suitable for small bites.
